{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775886316576,"sessionID":"ses_284f0e7efffeoJNYQHs4CBnkUX","part":{"id":"prt_d7b116547001lQRJFl7we5hB6A","messageID":"msg_d7b11411a0011kqMQDPWgTAvBt","sessionID":"ses_284f0e7efffeoJNYQHs4CBnkUX","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:29","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/VERIFICATION_REPORT_AR020.md","content":"# Verification Report: AR-020 CLI Pack Command\n\n**Module:** cmd/cli  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M  \n**Date:** 2026-04-11\n\n---\n\n## Executive Summary\n\n**Status: ✅ MOSTLY COMPLIANT**\n\nThe AR-020 CLI pack command implementation is **substantially complete** and functional. Core requirements for the pack command are implemented correctly. However, several service provider files mentioned in the spec are missing (placeholder stubs), and example agents are not present.\n\n---\n\n## Package Layout Verification\n\n### ✅ Compliant Files\n\n| Path | Spec Requirement | Status | Notes |\n|------|-----------------|--------|-------|\n| `pyproject.toml` | Project metadata, dependencies, console script mapping | ✅ PASS | Correctly configured with `kubectl-agentcube` entry point |\n| `agentcube/__init__.py` | Package version `__version__`, exports `app`, runtimes | ✅ PASS | Exports `app`, `PackRuntime`, `BuildRuntime`, `PublishRuntime`, `InvokeRuntime` |\n| `agentcube/cli/__init__.py` | CLI subpackage marker | ✅ PASS | Contains module docstring |\n| `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Typer `app`, all commands, `_handle_error`, `version_callback` | ✅ PASS | All required functions present, properly structured |\n| `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | `MetadataOptions` dataclass | ✅ PASS | Full implementation with `from_options()` class method |\n| `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | Re-exports runtimes + `MetadataOptions` | ✅ PASS | All 6 items exported correctly |\n| `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` | `PackRuntime` | ✅ PASS | Full implementation with 8-step pack workflow |\n| `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` | `BuildRuntime` | ⚠️ PARTIAL | Stub exists but not fully implemented |\n| `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | `PublishRuntime` | ⚠️ PARTIAL | Stub exists but not fully implemented |\n| `agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py` | `InvokeRuntime` | ⚠️ PARTIAL | Stub exists but not fully implemented |\n| `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | `StatusRuntime` | ⚠️ PARTIAL | Stub exists but not fully implemented |\n| `agentcube/services/__init__.py` | Services package docstring | ✅ PASS | Contains comprehensive docstring |\n| `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | `AgentMetadata`, `MetadataService` | ✅ PASS | Pydantic models with validators, full CRUD operations |\n| `agentcube/operations/__init__.py` | Placeholder module docstring | ✅ PASS | Contains module docstring |\n\n### ❌ Missing Files\n\n| Path | Spec Requirement | Status | Impact |\n|------|-----------------|--------|--------|\n| `agentcube/services/docker_service.py` | `DockerService` | ❌ MISSING | Required for build/publish operations |\n| `agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py` | `KubernetesProvider` | ❌ MISSING | Required for K8s deployments |\n| `agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py` | `AgentCubeProvider` | ❌ MISSING | Required for AgentCube platform integration |\n| `examples/hello-agent/main.py` | Example agent | ❌ MISSING | Documentation/example gap |\n| `examples/math-agent/main.py` | Example agent | ❌ MISSING | Documentation/example gap |\n\n---\n\n## Console Script Entry Point Verification\n\n### Spec Requirement\n```toml\n[project.scripts]\nkubectl-agentcube = \"agentcube.cli.main:app\"\n```\n\n### Implementation\n```toml\n[project.scripts]\nkubectl-agentcube = \"agentcube.cli.main:app\"\n```\n\n**Status: ✅ PASS**\n\n---\n\n## Typer App Configuration Verification\n\n### Spec Requirement\n```python\napp = typer.Typer(\n    name=\"agentcube\",\n    help=\"...\",\n    no_args_is_help=True,\n    rich_markup_mode=\"rich\",\n    add_completion=False\n)\n```\n\n### Implementation (lines 19-25)\n```python\napp = typer.Typer(\n    name=\"agentcube\",\n    help=\"AgentCube CLI - A developer tool for AI agent lifecycle management\",\n    no_args_is_help=True,\n    rich_markup_mode=\"rich\",\n    add_completion=False,\n)\n```\n\n**Status: ✅ PASS** - All parameters match spec\n\n---\n\n## Root Callback Verification\n\n### Spec Requirement\n```python\ndef main(\n    version: Optional[bool] = typer.Option(\n        None, \"--version\", help=\"Show version and exit\",\n        callback=version_callback, is_eager=True,\n    ),\n    verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", \"-v\", help=\"Enable verbose output\"),\n) -> None:\n    \"\"\"AgentCube CLI - A developer tool for AI agent lifecycle management.\"\"\"\n```\n\n### Implementation (lines 56-69)\n```python\n@app.callback()\ndef main(\n    version: Optional[bool] = typer.Option(\n        None,\n        \"--version\",\n        help=\"Show version and exit\",\n        callback=version_callback,\n        is_eager=True,\n    ),\n    verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", \"-v\", help=\"Enable verbose output\"),\n) -> None:\n    \"\"\"AgentCube CLI - A developer tool for AI agent lifecycle management.\"\"\"\n    if verbose:\n        logging.basicConfig(level=logging.DEBUG)\n```\n\n**Status: ✅ PASS** - Callback signature matches spec, includes additional verbose logging setup\n\n---\n\n## Pack Command Verification\n\n### Spec Requirement Parameters\n```python\ndef pack(\n    workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\", ...),\n    agent_name: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--agent-name\", ...),\n    language: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--language\", ...),\n    entrypoint: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--entrypoint\", ...),\n    port: Optional[int] = typer.Option(None, ...),\n    ...\n) -> None:\n```\n\n### Implementation (lines 72-139)\n```python\n@app.command()\ndef pack(\n    workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\", ...),\n    agent_name: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--agent-name\", ...),\n    language: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--language\", ...),\n    entrypoint: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--entrypoint\", ...),\n    port: Optional[int] = typer.Option(None, \"--port\", ...),\n    build_mode: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--build-mode\", ...),\n    description: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--description\", ...),\n    output: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--output\", ...),\n    verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", ...),\n) -> None:\n    \"\"\"Pack an agent workspace for building and publishing.\"\"\"\n```\n\n**Status: ✅ PASS** - All required parameters present, with additional `build_mode`, `description`, `output`, and `verbose` options\n\n---\n\n## PackRuntime Implementation Verification\n\n### Core Methods Implemented\n\n| Method | Status | Description |\n|--------|--------|-------------|\n| `__init__(verbose)` | ✅ | Initializes logger and MetadataService |\n| `pack(workspace, **options)` | ✅ | Main 8-step pack workflow |\n| `_validate_workspace_structure()` | ✅ | Validates workspace exists and is directory |\n| `_load_or_create_metadata()` | ✅ | Loads or creates metadata with precedence |\n| `_apply_option_overrides()` | ✅ | Applies CLI overrides to metadata |\n| `_validate_language_compatibility()` | ✅ | Python/Java validation |\n| `_process_dependencies()` | ✅ | requirements.txt/pom.xml processing |\n| `_generate_dockerfile()` | ✅ | Python/Java Dockerfile generation |\n| `_update_pack_metadata()` | ✅ | Updates metadata with pack timestamp |\n| `_prepare_output_path()` | ✅ | Resolves output path |\n| `_infer_entrypoint()` | ✅ | Auto-detects entrypoint from workspace |\n\n**Status: ✅ PASS** - Full implementation with comprehensive functionality\n\n---\n\n## MetadataOptions Dataclass Verification\n\n### Fields Implemented\n\n| Field | Type | Default | Status |\n|-------|------|---------|--------|\n| agent_name | Optional[str] | None | ✅ |\n| language | Optional[str] | \"python\" | ✅ |\n| entrypoint | Optional[str] | None | ✅ |\n| port | Optional[int] | 8080 | ✅ |\n| build_mode | Optional[str] | \"local\" | ✅ |\n| requirements_file | Optional[str] | None | ✅ |\n| description | Optional[str] | None | ✅ |\n| workload_manager_url | Optional[str] | \"\" | ✅ |\n| router_url | Optional[str] | \"\" | ✅ |\n| readiness_probe_path | Optional[str] | \"\" | ✅ |\n| readiness_probe_port | Optional[int] | 8080 | ✅ |\n| registry_url | Optional[str] | \"\" | ✅ |\n| registry_username | Optional[str] | \"\" | ✅ |\n| registry_password | Optional[str] | \"\" | ✅ |\n| agent_endpoint | Optional[str] | \"\" | ✅ |\n\n**Status: ✅ PASS** - All fields present with `from_options()` factory method\n\n---\n\n## AgentMetadata Model Verification\n\n### Fields Implemented (metadata_service.py)\n\n| Field | Type | Status |\n|-------|------|--------|\n| agent_name | str (required) | ✅ |\n| description | Optional[str] | ✅ |\n| language | str | ✅ |\n| entrypoint | str (required) | ✅ |\n| port | int | ✅ |\n| build_mode | str | ✅ |\n| region | Optional[str] | ✅ |\n| version | Optional[str] | ✅ |\n| image | Optional[Dict] | ✅ |\n| auth | Optional[Dict] | ✅ |\n| requirements_file | Optional[str] | ✅ |\n| registry_url | Optional[str] | ✅ |\n| registry_username | Optional[str] | ✅ |\n| registry_password | Optional[str] | ✅ |\n| agent_endpoint | Optional[str] | ✅ |\n| workload_manager_url | Optional[str] | ✅ |\n| router_url | Optional[str] | ✅ |\n| readiness_probe_path | Optional[str] | ✅ |\n| readiness_probe_port | Optional[int] | ✅ |\n| agent_id | Optional[str] | ✅ |\n| session_id | Optional[str] | ✅ |\n| k8s_deployment | Optional[Dict] | ✅ |\n| pack_timestamp | Optional[str] | ✅ |\n| dockerfile_generated | Optional[bool] | ✅ |\n\n### Validators\n\n| Validator | Status |\n|-----------|--------|\n| `validate_language()` | ✅ |\n| `vali